This paper discusses the use of automatic differentiation in computational statistics, which involves numerical methods and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SC (Scientific Computing), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
